      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRANCING PAT (1) has a strong record this track and trip including five wins from five starts. Recorded a 5 length win (18.49) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Looks a leading chance on best. BRACE FOR KAOS (2) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Grade 5 win two back (18.45) at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. QUARTIC FUNCTION (8) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 18.45 beating SILVERTREE BRAD. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. IN THE KLONDIKE (4) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
